long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Invaluable to anyone using the Natterbox CTI and Webphone products: scans your tabs for phone numbers and converts them to links that initiate a call on the CTI when clicked, and puts your CTI in focus when the call starts.

Please note - this extension is for Natterbox customers only, and has no effect unless you are using a Natterbox CTI.
